---
<section class="relative h-screen bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/pet-hero.jpg');">
    <!-- Overlay con degradado utilizando colores de la marca -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#5E388D]/70 to-[#4DBECD]/60"></div>
  
    <!-- Contenido centrado -->
    <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center h-full text-center px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center mb-16 mt-10">
          <button class="group relative transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 mb-4">
            <img src="/open_pet.png" alt="OpenPet Logo" class="h-20 cursor-pointer" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#5E388D]/0 group-hover:bg-[#5E388D]/10 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300"></div>
          </button>
          <button class="download-btn group relative bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 p-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(245,157,7,0.5)] border border-white/10">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white group-hover:text-[#F59D07] transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
            </svg>
            <span class="sr-only">Descargar app</span>
            <!-- Tooltip -->
            <div class="absolute -top-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bg-[#5E388D] text-white text-xs py-1 px-2 rounded opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 whitespace-nowrap pointer-events-none shadow-lg">
              Descargar aplicación
              <svg class="absolute text-[#5E388D] h-2 w-full left-0 top-full" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 255 255"><polygon class="fill-current" points="0,0 127.5,127.5 255,0"></polygon></svg>
            </div>
          </button>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white font-['Montserrat',_sans-serif] leading-tight">
          <span class="block">Cuida de los que más quieres</span>
          <span class="text-[#F59D07]">de forma inteligente</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-100 mb-8 font-light">
          Tu compañero digital para el cuidado de mascotas. Registra, organiza y recuerda todo lo que tu mascota necesita para una vida feliz y saludable.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/about" class="bg-[#F59D07] hover:bg-[#F59D07]/80 text-white font-medium py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg shadow-md">
            Conocer más
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-md text-white font-medium py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg border border-white/30 shadow-md">
            Contáctanos
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

<style>
  /* Animación para el botón de descarga */
  @keyframes pulse {
    0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(245, 157, 7, 0.4); }
    70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(245, 157, 7, 0); }
    100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(245, 157, 7, 0); }
  }
  
  .download-btn {
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .download-btn:hover {
    animation: none;
  }
</style>